{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121",
    "translationId": "rus-synodal",
    "bookSlug": "psalms",
    "chapterNumber": 121,
    "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121",
    "summary": "Source text for Psalms 121 in Russian Synodal Translation."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.1",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:1",
      "text": "Возрадовался я, когда сказали мне: \"пойдем в дом Господень\".",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.2",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:2",
      "text": "Вот, стоят ноги наши во вратах твоих, Иерусалим, -",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.3",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:3",
      "text": "Иерусалим, устроенный как город, слитый в одно,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.4",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:4",
      "text": "куда восходят колена, колена Господни, по закону Израилеву, славить имя Господне.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.5",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:5",
      "text": "Там стоят престолы суда, престолы дома Давидова.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.6",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:6",
      "text": "Просите мира Иерусалиму: да благоденствуют любящие тебя!",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.7",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:7",
      "text": "Да будет мир в стенах твоих, благоденствие - в чертогах твоих!",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.8",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:8",
      "text": "Ради братьев моих и ближних моих говорю я: \"мир тебе!\"",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rus-synodal:psalms.121.9",
      "translationId": "rus-synodal",
      "bookSlug": "psalms",
      "chapterNumber": 121,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Psalms 121:9",
      "text": "Ради дома Господа, Бога нашего, желаю блага тебе.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
